ğŸ§  4. Key Differences Explained

ğŸ”¹ Decision Making

* Traditional AI only responds
* Agentic AI **chooses actions**

---

ğŸ”¹ Memory

* Traditional AI forgets after response
* Agentic AI remembers context

---

ğŸ”¹ Tool Usage

* Traditional AI does not call APIs
* Agentic AI can use tools, databases, files

---

ğŸ”¹ Planning

* Traditional AI answers directly
* Agentic AI breaks tasks into steps

